{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, whenever they came, we had to hide our weapons, because we were always afraid that they might take it away saying that they are a military group, and they need it for themselves.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as much as we welcomed them, we were afraid of them, that they might strip us from-- my uncle was afraid that they might take the weapons away from us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were there, and there was military action against the Germans by the partisans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I mentioned, the war wasn't- wasn't going that well for them any longer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it became sort of safer to be in the woods, because we haven't heard for a long time of any searches or attacks after that period.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my uncle decided it was safe enough to perhaps make a permanent home for the winter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went, and he built this house with this other young man and his mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And already at that time, my uncle owned a horse, and we had a cow that we were able to milk for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Milk.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had enough food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no problem, and we didn't have to go begging for food any longer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle provided, through his contacts, enough food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we moved into to the new house there, before long, there was a full house of people, because everybody that showed up, my aunt had mercy on them, and she took them in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we were in the house, I would say perhaps 14 people in not too long a time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived in that house until February '94, when we were liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
